Millions of Britons are struggling to get by after energy bills more than doubled last year, but the cost of living crisis is often much worse for disabled people. Some Britons with disabilities or health conditions have no choice but to run vital equipment that uses electricity meaning their bills are even higher and some are having to make impossible choices.       Anne asked John to donate the money to fuel poverty charity National Energy Action instead.  People who are struggling could be dueÂ cost of living help and energy bill support on these key dates during 2023.  